1. Durable AI
Category: Website Builder

Instantly build a complete business website in under 30 seconds.

Just enter a business name, and Durable AI generates the design, content, and layout.

Great for entrepreneurs and freelancers.

Free tier available with limited editing.

2. Papercup
Category: AI Voice Dubbing / Video Localization

Upload your video and get AI-generated voiceovers in multiple languages.

Ideal for content creators and educators expanding to international audiences.

Free version available with watermark and usage limits.

3. Talk to Books
Category: AI-powered Research Tool (by Google AI)

Ask any question and get real responses quoted from thousands of books.

Amazing tool for deep thinkers, researchers, and curious minds.

Completely free with no signup needed.

